Package di.unipi.matchmaker Description

Package which provides a prototype implementation of the (exact and plug-in) matchmakers proposed in: "A. Brogi, J. Soldani. Matching cloud services with TOSCA. In Proceedings of FOCLASA '13, Springer, 2013."
Copyright 2013 Jacopo Soldani (Computer Science department, University of Pisa)
Version:
1.0
Author:
